          Est. 2022 â€¢ Pharmacist-Founded
        </Badge>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
          Meet the Team Behind <span class="text-nbs-primary">NBS Supplements</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-muted-foreground mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          We're four passionate pharmacists who got tired of seeing an industry full of 
          <span class="text-nbs-accent font-semibold">empty promises and proprietary blends</span>. 
          So we decided to do something about it.
        </p>

        <!-- Team Photo Placeholder -->
        <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-nbs-primary/10 to-nbs-secondary/10 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-nbs-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 text-nbs-primary/30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
