            with complete transparency. Every ingredient has a purpose, every dose is clinically backed, 
            and every claim is backed by science.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Company Story Sections -->
    <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        
        <!-- Why We Started NBS -->
        <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
                Why We Started NBS
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  After years of working in pharmacy and seeing what goes into most supplements, 
                  we were honestly disgusted. <span class="text-nbs-accent font-semibold">Proprietary blends</span> that hide 
                  underdosed ingredients. <span class="text-nbs-accent font-semibold">Artificial fillers</span> that serve no purpose 
                  except to bulk up capsules. <span class="text-nbs-accent font-semibold">Marketing claims</span> with zero scientific backing.
                </p>
                <p>
                  We knew there had to be a better way. As pharmacists, we understand bioavailability, 
                  drug interactions, and what actually works at the cellular level. We decided to use 
                  that knowledge to create supplements we'd actually give to our own families.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-nbs-primary font-semibold">NBS isn't just another supplement company</span> â€“ 
                  we're pharmacists first, entrepreneurs second. Every decision we make is filtered through 
                  our training and our commitment to "do no harm."
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
