                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Philosophy -->
        <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-nbs-secondary/10 to-nbs-natural/10 rounded-2xl border border-nbs-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <svg class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 text-nbs-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
                </svg>
                <p class="text-nbs-secondary font-semibold">Natural First</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">But effective always</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
                Our Philosophy: Natural is Best
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  We believe your body knows the difference between natural and synthetic ingredients. 
                  That's why we source <span class="text-nbs-secondary font-semibold">natural compounds</span> whenever possible â€“ 
                  from guarana extract instead of synthetic caffeine to monk fruit instead of artificial sweeteners.
                </p>
                <p>
                  But "natural" doesn't mean "weak." Every natural ingredient we choose is backed by clinical research 
                  and dosed at levels that actually work. We're not interested in fairy dusting or feel-good marketing.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-nbs-primary font-semibold">Transparency is non-negotiable.</span> We list every ingredient 
                  and its exact dose on our labels. No proprietary blends, no hidden fillers, no surprises. 
                  If you can't pronounce it or don't know why it's there, we probably won't use it.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">
              What Makes Us Different
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              We're not just another supplement company. We're pharmacists who happen to make supplements.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Expert Knowledge -->
            <Card class="text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
              <CardHeader>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-nbs-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-nbs-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
