                <CardTitle class="text-xl">Transparent Formulations</CardTitle>
                <CardDescription>Every ingredient and dose clearly labeled</CardDescription>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                  No proprietary blends or hidden formulas. You know exactly what you're getting 
                  and why each ingredient is included.
                </p>
              </CardContent>
